ðŸŽ¯ Project Goals & Objectives

Provide a centralized platform for online product discovery and purchasing.

Offer secure user authentication and authorization.

Enable real-time cart and inventory management.

Simplify order processing and transaction handling.

Allow administrators to manage products and monitor activity.

Ensure responsive design for mobile and desktop devices.

Build with a modular and scalable architecture for future enhancements.

